Description: Guitar is in excellent shape, near mint. No visible scratches or dings, no issues. I've attempted to show the lack of fretwear in the photos. I'm more into solid body guitars, I just haven't played it enough to keep it. There are a couple of small scratches on the case, none go through the Tolex. This guitar sounds great, but my wife makes me sell one when I buy another. This guitar sells for $1199 new on Sweetwater. Case candy is included. I've had this guitar about a 8 months and all I've done to it is change the strings. More pics are available on request, just let me know what you'd like to see.
